Articles.Content: The status bar on the loading screen gets stuck on "KWLmengineMaverick1D". What do I do?

Possibly running out of memory, you need to provide your log file (check this post http://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/83212-how-to-get-support-read-first/&do=findComment&comment=1368573) and a list of mods you are using.

Also do you have the community patches for KW installed?

Thank you, 

All I needed was the Community Fixes patch. I must not have seen that as a requirement when I downloaded the original mod. Thanks again!
